# !Pitch

## Created By: Sharon Maswai

## Description:

This a web app that allows a user to sign up, login in once authenticated then post a pitch in a category of their choice. They also get to comment on other other pitches and also views the comments on their own pitches

## BDD

| Behaviour | Input  | Output |
| -- |-- |--|
|Registration of user| Click sign up | Redirects to registration page|
|User logging in|Click sign in|Redirects to sign-in page|
|View Pitches|Click view pitches button|Redirects to posts page|
|Add a new Pitch|Click on add pitch button|Redirects to Pitches form page|



## Bugs

There were no known bugs by the time of deployment.


## Technologies used

HTML

CSS

Python3.6

Flask

Bootstrap 4




## Running app

In the terminal:

$ ./start.sh

